OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777810266
OL,3,CMoment police use 'specialist tactics'
OL,4,Cto force 100mph driver to a stop
OL,6,FPolice have released footage of the
OL,7,Fmoment they force a dangerous driver
OL,8,Ftravelling at more than 100mph to a
OL,9,Fstop on the A23 in Brighton.
OL,11,FOfficers used specialist vehicle
OL,12,Ftactics to stop Alexander Morris, 46,
OL,13,Ffrom Reading - boxing him in in his
OL,14,Fblack Mercedes C180 at the side of the
OL,15,Fcarriageway.
OL,17,FMorris, unemployed, of Mill Green,
OL,18,FCaversham, was arrested and taken into
OL,19,Fcustody, where he failed to give an
OL,20,Fevidential blood sample for drugs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
