PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777810266
OL,3,CMoment police use 'specialist tactics'
OL,4,Cto force 100mph driver to a stop
OL,6,FHe was charged with driving without
OL,7,Fdue care and attention, failing to
OL,8,Fprovide a specimen of blood for
OL,9,Fanalysis, possession of cannabis,
OL,10,Fdriving without a licence and driving
OL,11,Fwithout insurance.
OL,13,FMorris admitted all offences and
OL,14,Fappeared before Crawley Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt on Tuesday 21 April, where he
OL,16,Fwas disqualified from driving for 18
OL,17,Fmonths, fined #400 fine and ordered to
OL,18,Fpay a #160 victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
