FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777810266
OL,3,CMoment police use 'specialist tactics'
OL,4,Cto force 100mph driver to a stop
OL,6,FInspector Ollie Pullen, of Operations
OL,7,FCommand, said: "The defendant showed a
OL,8,Fcomplete disregard for other road
OL,9,Fusers through his manner of driving.
OL,11,F"When officers attempted to stop the
OL,12,Fvehicle, he tried to evade police.
OL,14,F"Morris also failed a roadside drug
OL,15,Ftest, indicating he may have been
OL,16,Fdriving under the influence and over
OL,17,Fthe prescribed limit, he subsequently
OL,18,Ffailed to provide an evidential sample
OL,19,Ffollowing his arrest.
