PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777810266
OL,3,CMoment police use 'specialist tactics'
OL,4,Cto force 100mph driver to a stop
OL,6,F"Let this serve as a reminder that
OL,7,Fanyone intent on using our road
OL,8,Fnetwork to commit crime, or to drive
OL,9,Fwhile under the influence, should be
OL,10,Funder no illusion that - where
OL,11,Fproportionate - we will continue to
OL,12,Fuse vehicle tactics to target
OL,13,Foffenders and keep all road users
OL,14,Fsafe."
